name: RETROJET - United Airlines "Friend Ship" A320-232 [N475UA] Takeoff from Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Today, United just happened to send their A320 retrojet to YYC on their daily rotation to and from Houston George Bush Intercontinental Airport. Great to see this livery, and especially in that light! ATC is included, enjoy!

Thanks for watching!
